WEBVTT

00:04:56.957 --> 00:05:02.347
It's the lack of recognition
of their skilled occupations.

00:05:03.048 --> 00:05:07.044
The bank systems and structures
have no means to recognize them

00:05:07.068 --> 00:05:08.556
as micro-businesses,

00:05:08.580 --> 00:05:11.158
much less the fact that, you know,

00:05:11.182 --> 00:05:13.390
her tree doesn't have
a forwarding address.

00:05:13.912 --> 00:05:16.238
So she's trapped in the middle.

00:05:16.262 --> 00:05:18.693
She's falling through the cracks
of our assumptions.

00:05:18.717 --> 00:05:22.256
You know all those microloans
to help African women traders?

00:05:22.646 --> 00:05:25.476
They're going to loan her
50 dollars or 100 dollars.

00:05:25.500 --> 00:05:27.106
What's she going to do with it?

00:05:27.130 --> 00:05:29.472
She spends 10 times
that amount every month

00:05:29.496 --> 00:05:31.098
just on inventory --